properties.name: compatibility
properties.description: What Illustrator file format version to create.

properties.name: embedLinkedFiles
properties.description: Are linked image files to be included in the saved document.

properties.name: includeDocumentThumbnails
properties.description: Include thumbnail image of the EPS artwork.

properties.name: embedAllFonts
properties.description: Embed all fonts used by the document in the saved file (version 7 or later)

properties.name: postScript
properties.description: PostScript level to use (level 1 valid for file format version 8 or older)

properties.name: flattenOutput
properties.description: How should transparency be flattened for older file format versions (pre-version 9)

properties.name: compatibleGradientPrinting
properties.description: Create a raster item of the gradient or gradient mesh so that PostScript Level 2 printers can print the object.

properties.name: saveMultipleArtboards
properties.description: All the artboards or range of the artboards will be saved.

properties.name: artboardRange
properties.description: If SaveMultipleArtboards is true,this will be considered for multi-asset extraction which specifies artboard range.Empty string will extracts all the artboards.Default is empty string.

name: EPSSaveOptions
description: Options which may be supplied when saving a document as an Illustrator EPS file.
